Aku belum pernah memasak

726
00:38:11,120 --> 00:38:13,449
sup kue beras dengan gula seperti ini.

727
00:38:13,819 --> 00:38:14,850
Bi Cho.

728
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:44,579
Anting-anting itu tampak baru.

729
00:38:45,250 --> 00:38:46,889
Apa Bu Oh memberikannya kepada Anda juga?

730
00:38:47,350 --> 00:38:48,389
Ya.

731
00:38:49,519 --> 00:38:52,019
Anda tampak cantik mengenakan apa pun.

732
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:58,359
Da Ya.

