743
00:39:57,859 --> 00:39:59,389
Dasar pencuri.

744
00:39:59,389 --> 00:40:01,460
Kamu belajar mencuri dari ibumu?

745
00:40:01,460 --> 00:40:02,900
Dasar wanita licik.

746
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:06,000
Nenek, tolong lepaskan aku.

