00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,940
- Jangan.
- Astaga.

752
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:17,939
Da Ya, kaburlah.

753
00:40:17,939 --> 00:40:20,379
Myeong Hee, wanita licik ini

