00:45:51,239 --> 00:45:54,550
Ibu, aku kemari karena kesal.

853
00:45:54,550 --> 00:45:56,979
Apa yang terjadi kali ini?

854
00:45:57,649 --> 00:46:01,320
Ibu dan nenek mertuaku...

855
00:46:01,749 --> 00:46:03,060
Astaga.

856
00:46:03,560 --> 00:46:05,019
Suara apa ini?

857
00:46:06,129 --> 00:46:07,989
Mi Ran, kamu di dapur?

858
00:46:10,399 --> 00:46:11,529
Mi Ran.

